    {
      "id": "transform-why",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 803.36328125,
      "y": 676.50390625,
      "width": 407.97943115234375,
      "height": 34.92578125,
      "fontSize": 13.970312499999999,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "WHY: Merge technical metadata (Glue schemas, LF-Tags)\n with business context,generate embeddings for semantic search",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#43a047",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 8,
      "version": 202,
      "versionNonce": 489785832,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774459270629,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "a7",
      "angle": 0,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WHY: Merge technical metadata (Glue schemas, LF-Tags)\n with business context,generate embeddings for semantic search",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "transform-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1557.42578125,
      "y": 490.72265625,
      "width": 980,
      "height": 300,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Step 1: Parse semantic.yaml → UnifiedMetadataGraph (Python dataclasses)\n\nStep 2: Fetch Glue Data Catalog → Add actual column types (decimal, varchar, etc.)\n\nStep 3: Fetch Lake Formation LF-Tags → Add PII_Classification, Data_Sensitivity tags\n\nStep 4: Generate Titan Embeddings (AWS Bedrock)\n   • Table embeddings: \"positions table stores portfolio positions with market value\"\n   • Column embeddings: \"market_value is a sum measure representing portfolio value\"\n   • Business term embeddings: \"Market Value\" = \"AUM\" = \"Assets Under Management\"\n   → 1024-dimensional vectors (cosine similarity for semantic search)\n\nStep 5: Convert to Neptune Gremlin format\n   • Vertices: Database, Table, Column, BusinessTerm (with embedding property)\n   • Edges: contains, has_column, references (FK), described_by\n\nStep 6: Create SynoDB DynamoDB table → Store seed SQL queries with embeddings\n\nStep 7: Load to Neptune → Bulk insert via neptune-load API",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 9,
      "version": 198,
      "versionNonce": 1615680664,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774458818049,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "a8",
      "angle": 0,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 1: Parse semantic.yaml → UnifiedMetadataGraph (Python dataclasses)\n\nStep 2: Fetch Glue Data Catalog → Add actual column types (decimal, varchar, etc.)\n\nStep 3: Fetch Lake Formation LF-Tags → Add PII_Classification, Data_Sensitivity tags\n\nStep 4: Generate Titan Embeddings (AWS Bedrock)\n   • Table embeddings: \"positions table stores portfolio positions with market value\"\n   • Column embeddings: \"market_value is a sum measure representing portfolio value\"\n   • Business term embeddings: \"Market Value\" = \"AUM\" = \"Assets Under Management\"\n   → 1024-dimensional vectors (cosine similarity for semantic search)\n\nStep 5: Convert to Neptune Gremlin format\n   • Vertices: Database, Table, Column, BusinessTerm (with embedding property)\n   • Edges: contains, has_column, references (FK), described_by\n\nStep 6: Create SynoDB DynamoDB table → Store seed SQL queries with embeddings\n\nStep 7: Load to Neptune → Bulk insert via neptune-load API",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.214574898785425
    },
