    {
      "id": "neptune-why",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 138.625,
      "y": 941.875,
      "width": 658.0720825195312,
      "height": 16.25,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "WHY: Graph structure lets AI traverse relationships (FK → JOIN) and find similar tables/columns via embeddings",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#7b1fa2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 15,
      "version": 129,
      "versionNonce": 515019496,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774459160837,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "aE",
      "angle": 0,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WHY: Graph structure lets AI traverse relationships (FK → JOIN) and find similar tables/columns via embeddings",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "neptune-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 130,
      "y": 1160,
      "width": 940,
      "height": 460,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "STORED IN NEPTUNE:\n\nVERTICES (Nodes):\n  Database vertex:\n    id: 'financial_portfolios_db'\n    name: 'financial_portfolios_db'\n    workload: 'financial_portfolios'\n  \n  Table vertex:\n    id: 'financial_portfolios_db.positions'\n    name: 'positions'\n    type: 'fact'\n    grain: 'one row per position per date'\n    embedding: [0.123, 0.456, ..., 0.789]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n  \n  Column vertex:\n    id: 'positions.market_value'\n    name: 'market_value'\n    data_type: 'decimal(18,2)'              ← From Glue Catalog\n    role: 'measure'                         ← From semantic.yaml\n    default_aggregation: 'sum'              ← From semantic.yaml\n    pii_classification: 'NONE'              ← From Lake Formation LF-Tags\n    data_sensitivity: 'PUBLIC'              ← From Lake Formation LF-Tags\n    embedding: [0.234, 0.567, ..., 0.890]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n  \n  BusinessTerm vertex:\n    id: 'term:Market Value'\n    term: 'Market Value'\n    synonyms: ['AUM', 'Assets Under Management', 'Portfolio Value']\n    embedding: [0.345, 0.678, ..., 0.901]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n\nEDGES (Relationships - queryable via Gremlin):\n  Database --contains--> Table\n  Table --has_column--> Column\n  Column --references--> Column (foreign key relationship)\n  Column --described_by--> BusinessTerm\n\nGREMLIN QUERY EXAMPLE:\n  g.V('positions.portfolio_id')        # Start at FK column\n    .outE('references').inV()          # Follow FK edge\n    .inE('has_column').outV()          # Get parent table\n  → Result: portfolios table\n  → AI auto-generates: JOIN portfolios ON positions.portfolio_id = portfolios.portfolio_id",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 16,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1178812904,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774458435024,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "aF",
      "angle": 0,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STORED IN NEPTUNE:\n\nVERTICES (Nodes):\n  Database vertex:\n    id: 'financial_portfolios_db'\n    name: 'financial_portfolios_db'\n    workload: 'financial_portfolios'\n  \n  Table vertex:\n    id: 'financial_portfolios_db.positions'\n    name: 'positions'\n    type: 'fact'\n    grain: 'one row per position per date'\n    embedding: [0.123, 0.456, ..., 0.789]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n  \n  Column vertex:\n    id: 'positions.market_value'\n    name: 'market_value'\n    data_type: 'decimal(18,2)'              ← From Glue Catalog\n    role: 'measure'                         ← From semantic.yaml\n    default_aggregation: 'sum'              ← From semantic.yaml\n    pii_classification: 'NONE'              ← From Lake Formation LF-Tags\n    data_sensitivity: 'PUBLIC'              ← From Lake Formation LF-Tags\n    embedding: [0.234, 0.567, ..., 0.890]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n  \n  BusinessTerm vertex:\n    id: 'term:Market Value'\n    term: 'Market Value'\n    synonyms: ['AUM', 'Assets Under Management', 'Portfolio Value']\n    embedding: [0.345, 0.678, ..., 0.901]  ← 1024-dim Titan vector\n\nEDGES (Relationships - queryable via Gremlin):\n  Database --contains--> Table\n  Table --has_column--> Column\n  Column --references--> Column (foreign key relationship)\n  Column --described_by--> BusinessTerm\n\nGREMLIN QUERY EXAMPLE:\n  g.V('positions.portfolio_id')        # Start at FK column\n    .outE('references').inV()          # Follow FK edge\n    .inE('has_column').outV()          # Get parent table\n  → Result: portfolios table\n  → AI auto-generates: JOIN portfolios ON positions.portfolio_id = portfolios.portfolio_id",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.8914728682170542
    },
    {
      "id": "synodb-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1197.08984375,
