      "height": 80,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "NOT STORED (queried live via MCP):\n  • Glue Catalog: Table schemas, column types, partitions, S3 locations\n  • Lake Formation LF-Tags: PII_Classification, Data_Sensitivity, Compliance tags\n  • Used during TRANSFORM step, not duplicated into Neptune",
